OGs remember Backseat Beat 🎤 @elainewelteroth is bringing it back, and this time with a message that’s bigger than beauty. 💋 

#MACVIVAGLAM is teaming up with her organization @birthfund along with their grant partner @thevictoriaprojectorg — two game-changing organizations that are redefining maternity care in America —one lipstick and one family at a time. Together, we’re funding full-spectrum, midwifery-led care for 38 underserved families – because no one should have to fight to survive childbirth.

ELEVATED IN ACTION. See how lifting + volumizing MACStack Elevated Mascara stacks on wispy lashes for a fanned-out effect in a flash that lasts…and LASTS: 

✔️+165% INSTANT LASH LIFT*. 
with 36-hour wear and a clump-proof coverage

✔️COATS LASHES FROM ROOTS TO TIPS
with a dual-sided Contour Lift Brush.

✔️NOURISHES LASHES
with a buildable, 91% naturally derived formula** featuring argan oil.

*Clinical testing on 32 people.
**Per ISO 16128 from plant sources, non-petroleum mineral sources and/or water.

latestPosts.caption:
THIS LIPSTICK CARES FOR WOMEN AND CHILDREN!
M·A·C VIVA GLAM is proud to kick off our newest non-profit partnership with @tvpthevictoriaproject and @birthfund with a $200,000 grant that will directly help: 

💄Fund holistic, midwifery-led services for 38 underserved US families
💄Expand access to safe, compassionate and personalized maternity care 
💄Ensure mothers receive the care they deserve without financial barriers 
💄Build a future where every family has access to the resources they need 

You can help us close the gap for birthing families — one birth, one family and one Lipstick at a time with four shades of #MACVIVAGLAM that give back 100% to charities supporting healthy futures and equal rights for all. 
 
@elainewelteroth
